'''高頻主動式極光研究項目'''（{{lang-en|High Frequency Active Auroral Research Program}}，常[[縮寫|縮寫]]為'''HAARP'''），是一個由[[美國空軍|美國空軍]]、[[美國海軍|美國海軍]]、[[國防高等研究計劃署|國防高等研究計劃署]]及[[阿拉斯加大學|阿拉斯加大學]]所共同合作的[[電離層|電離層]]研究計劃。{{R|FAQ Sheet}}{{R|Purpose}}HAARP計劃在[[阿拉斯加|阿拉斯加]]{{link-en|加科納|Gakona, Alaska}}設有一個由美國空軍負責管理的研究設施，被稱為HAARP研究站（HAARP Research Station）。
==历史==
*HAARP始建於1990年，由來自[[美國|美國]][[阿拉斯加州|阿拉斯加州]]的[[共和黨_(美國)|共和黨]]參議員特德·史蒂文斯幫助贏得了該設施的批准<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.nature.com/news/us-ionospheric-research-facility-to-close-1.15243|title = US ionospheric research facility to close|date = 16 May 2014|accessdate = 18 August 2014|website = Nature|publisher = Nature|last = Weinberger|first = Sharon|archive-date = 2017-10-17|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171017232221/http://www.nature.com/news/us-ionospheric-research-facility-to-close-1.15243|dead-url = no}}</ref>，並於1993年開始建設。
*2013年5月初，HAARP暫時關閉，等待更改其承包商以運營該設施。
*2013年7月，HAARP項目經理James Keeney表示，「[[國防高級研究計劃局|國防高級研究計劃局]]（DARPA）預計將作為客戶在2013年秋季至2014年冬季完成一些研究。<ref>{{cite web|title=HAARP Facility Shuts Down|url=http://www.arrl.org/news/view/haarp-facility-shuts-down|publisher=ARRL|accessdate=16 July 2013|archive-date=2018-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180827142354/http://www.arrl.org/news/view/haarp-facility-shuts-down|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="EarthSky">{{cite web|last=Byrd|first=Deborah|title=Crazy weather? You can't blame HAARP anymore|url=http://earthsky.org/earth/crazy-weather-you-cant-blame-haarp-anymore|publisher=EarthSky, 16 July 2013|accessdate=17 July 2013|archive-date=2018-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180827142329/http://earthsky.org/earth/crazy-weather-you-cant-blame-haarp-anymore|dead-url=no}}</ref>」而臨時停工則被描述為“承包商政權更迭”。 Ahtna和Incorporated是[[阿拉斯加|阿拉斯加]]本地的公司 ，服務於HAARP所在地的阿拉斯加州，據報導他們與Marsh Creek，LLC<ref name="AK">{{cite news|last=Anderson|first=Ben|title=Alaska's controversial HAARP facility closed – will it come back online?|url=http://www.alaskadispatch.com/article/20130717/alaska-s-controversial-haarp-facility-closed-will-it-come-back-online|accessdate=18 July 2013|newspaper=Alaska Dispatch|date=18 July 2013|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714064246/http://www.alaskadispatch.com/article/20130717/alaska-s-controversial-haarp-facility-closed-will-it-come-back-online|dead-url=no}}</ref>簽訂了設施管理合同。
*2014年5月，空軍宣布HAARP計劃將於2014年晚些時候關閉。<ref>{{cite news | title = Bye-Bye To The Home Of A Favorite Internet Conspiracy Theory | url = https://www.npr.org/2014/06/10/319539712/bye-bye-to-the-home-of-a-favorite-internet-conspiracy-theory | first = Geoff | last = Brumfiel | date = 10 June 2014 | work = NPR | accessdate = 2014-06-11 | archive-date = 2014-06-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140610230852/http://www.npr.org/2014/06/10/319539712/bye-bye-to-the-home-of-a-favorite-internet-conspiracy-theory | dead-url = no }}</ref>雖然實驗於2014年夏季結束，但該設施的完全關閉和拆除工作推遲至2015年5月。<ref>{{cite news | title = HAARP closure postponed until 2015 | url = http://www.adn.com/article/20140702/haarp-closure-postponed-until-2015 | first = Dermot | last = Cole | date = 2 July 2014 | work = Alaska Dispatch News | accessdate = 2015-06-03 | archive-date = 2015-05-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150527002742/http://www.adn.com/article/20140702/haarp-closure-postponed-until-2015 | dead-url = no }}</ref>
